summary: This course is for people who are new to the tech industry. You are going to have to watch these videos multiple times. It's not going to be easy. It shouldn't be easy. This is going to be a new beginning for you.
headline: This course is for people who are new to the tech industry.

summary: Imposter syndrome is when you forget that someone has been in the industry for a long time. Slow the information down. If you don't get it the first time, pause the videos afterwards. Ask yourself, what did i understand in this lesson?
headline: Ask yourself, what did i understand in this lesson?

summary: Watch the videos again. Engage with the video. Slow them down. Ask yourself, what did i learn? Pause and make it easy. Take a pause for at least 30 seconds to a minute. This is what i do with my students before we started learning.
headline: Engage with the video.

summary: All i want you to do is just close your eyes. Breathe in, breathe out. Now that you have breathed in, focus your attention on your heart. Keep relaxing. Just calm feel the flow of energy up and down. Clear your brain and relax. Nothing to think about. I ain't going to do it for a minute but you all do it for a minute. I'll see you in the next video. Deuces.
headline: Just calm feel the flow of energy up and down.
